Hey everyone!

The CrapNAT™ storage thread didn't go as well as @maldovia was hoping, but in any case, I thought I'd give away 4x 500GB plans.

For those who don't know what CrapNAT™ is, it's a free initiative offering NAT VPSes with 0% SLA and no guaranteed support. It's funded through donations and is available to LET users who have held accounts (with good reputation) for 6 months or more.

You can learn more about it [here](https://clients.hadrill.co.uk/knowledgebase.php?action=displayarticle&amp;id=2).

The four servers that are available will have the following specs:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt; 1 vCPU&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; 256MB RAM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; 500GB HDD (no raid, no backups)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; 1TB BW @ 1 Gbps (shared port)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; Hosted at Online.net in France&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
VMs automatically expire after 30 days but can be extended by throwing in a ticket (provided you get in touch in plenty of time).

I'd ideally like to keep the 500GB plans to donators, but that is by no means a rule.

As always, donations are always welcome [here](https://clients.hadrill.co.uk/knowledgebase.php?action=displayarticle&amp;id=4). The service is currently funded until sometime in May. 

Drop me a PM if you're interested, I'll try and sort out any requests on a first come first-served basis (provided you fit the criteria) later tonight else tomorrow :-)


Happy crapping!
